==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tilter
<hw>Tilt"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
tilts, or jousts; hence, one who fights.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Let me alone to match your <qex>tilter</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Glanville.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who operates a tilt hammer.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tilth</ent>⟦br⟧
